images:
A highly detailed, technical blueprint-style developer infographic poster on the theme of "ENTERPRISE GUARDRAILS FRAMEWORK".
Overall Theme: High-tech dark mode developer dashboard, cybersecurity blueprint, with sharp glowing lines and neat borders.
Colors: Deep dark navy background with glowing neon blue, electric cyan, warning red, and success green highlights.

Header:
- A prominent top-center glowing blue header: "ENTERPRISE GUARDRAILS FRAMEWORK".
- Below it, a clean subtitle: "Confidence Gates, Idempotency, and Human Review for gpt-5.5 + Salesforce" with a small Salesforce logo on the top-left and an "APEX BEST PRACTICES" badge on the top-right.

Section 1: "WHY IT MATTERS" (Top Row, 3 Horizontal Cards)
- "Confidence Gate" with a filter icon, "Idempotency" with a key icon, "Human Loop" with a person icon

Section 2: "THE COST" (Middle Row, Side-by-Side Comparison)
- Left Box (Red Theme): "NO GUARDRAILS — Dangerous at Enterprise Scale". Shows a red status pill "DANGER — ANTI-PATTERN".
- Right Box (Green Theme): "GUARDRAILS ACTIVE — Confidence + Idempotency + Audit". Shows a green status pill "SUCCESS — BEST PRACTICE".

Section 3: "CODE PATTERNS" (Main Center)
- Left Column (Bad Code in Red Border):
  - Heading: "// BAD"
  - Code block:
    // Agent calls Salesforce directly — no safety net
const agent = new OpenAI.Agent({ tools: sfTools })
const result = await agent.run(caseInput)
// No confidence check. No idempotency.
// No audit log. No human escalation path.
- Right Column (Good Code in Green Border):
  - Heading: "// GOOD"
  - Code block:
    if (result.confidence < 0.85) {
  return escalateToHuman(result, reason)
}
if (await idempotencyLog.exists(key)) {
  return { status: 'ALREADY_APPLIED' }
}
await apexCommitService.apply(proposal)
await auditLog.record(result, 'COMMITTED')

Section 4: "DEVELOPER PROFILE & CHECKLIST" (Bottom Row)
- Left Side: A 3D Pixar-style cartoon avatar portrait of a dark-skinned South Asian male with a full thick black beard, shoulder-length wavy dark hair pulled up into a messy top bun, warm friendly smile showing teeth, wearing a grey crew-neck sweatshirt with the word "MAGNETIC" on it, set against a warm orange bokeh background. The avatar is labeled "Bennie Joseph | Salesforce Architect". Next to it is a quote bubble: "Architecting intuitive systems, engineering scalable solutions."
- Right Side: A checklist with points: "Confidence < 0.85 → human review, never auto-commit", "Check idempotency key before every Salesforce write", "Apex owns all DML — agent only returns proposals", "Log agent run ID, tools called, confidence, outcome", "Test with 200 records and concurrent saves".
- Footer: A thin bar with icons for "gpt-5.5", "Agentforce 2.0", "Apex v64.0", "Audit Safety" and the text "CODE SMART. AUTOMATE FASTER. DELIVER EXCELLENCE."

Style Details: Super high resolution, technical drawing grid, razor-sharp white and neon text, crisp layout, developer IDE aesthetic, flat vector graphics with subtle glow, highly legible monospace font for code blocks, professional presentation.
